{
    "chapter": 50,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "50:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>{戛弗}这在论述之前《黄牛》章起始的同类字母已经进行了解释。真主以尊贵的《古兰经》中的涵义、吉庆和祥瑞发誓，复活日，必将复活你们，以接受清算和报偿。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "50:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们拒绝的原因并不是料定你在撒谎，他们知道你是诚实的，而是因为他们奇怪，警告的使者竟是人类，而非精灵！他们诧异地说：“来临我们的使者是人类！这是件怪异的事情。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "50:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我们死后变成尘土会再复活？生命再次回到我们腐朽的身体？这真是不可思议的，绝不可能发生的事情！”</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "50:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我知道他们死后身体腐烂，大地对他们的身体蚕食，任何事务都不能对我隐藏，我这里有记录他们生前和死后事务的天经。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "50:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这些以物配主者否认使者带来的《古兰经》，他们处于混乱之中，因此他们无法确定任何事情。</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "50:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>“我创造诸天并以星辰加以点缀，且没有任何裂缝。难道这些否认复活者没有观测到吗？有能力创造天空者，也同样有能力复活死人。”</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "50:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我铺陈大地以适合你们居住，并在其中放置了预防其摇晃的山脉，生长着各种悦目的生物和植物。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "50:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我创造所有这些，只是为顺从主的仆人给予启发和教诲。</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "50:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我从天上降下大有裨益，受益良多的雨水，借此雨水生出果树和五谷，</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "50:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以及高耸挺拔、枝叶层叠的椰枣树。</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "50:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这些都是给予众仆食用的给养。我借雨水使不毛之地复活，如同我使复活死人一样。</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "50:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你的先前的人们也曾否认他们的先知，奴哈的宗族、水井的宗族（指今中亚阿塞拜疆地区的一个村落，当时他们的使者来临他们进行劝化，而他们将那使者投入一口井溺死，故他们被称为‘水井的宗族’）、赛莫德人，</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "50:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>阿德人、法老及鲁特的宗族、</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "50:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>舒阿卜的族人，即丛林的居民和也门图白的族人都曾否认了使者，故真主应诺的惩罚降临了他们。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "50:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道我有能力初次创造他们，却不能再次复活他们吗？他们对初造后的复活，确是处在怀疑之中。</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "50:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已创造了人类，知道他们内心的想法和思维，我离他们比他们颈部连接心脏的命脉还近。</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "50:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>位于左右边的两侧天使记录他的言行，</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "50:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他每说一句话都有天使进行现场记录。</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "50:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>濒死的痛苦将昭示真理，那时他无处可逃，对此忽视的人们啊！你不得后退，也无处可逃。</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "50:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当掌管号角的天使吹响第二声号角，即昭示复活日来临，那是曾给予不信道者警告的受罚之日。</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "50:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>每个人都由一位天使驱逐着，还有一位见证他们行为的天使同行。</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "50:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音对被驱逐者说：“在今世，你受你的欲望和享受所蒙蔽忽略了今天，我将以惩处和刑罚揭示你的忽略，今天你的眼光是锐利的，可以看到自己曾经所忽略的。”</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "50:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>受命陪伴他的天使说：“这是我所记录他的行为，丝毫不少，点滴不多。”</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "50:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主对驱逐和见证的两位天使说：“你们俩把他扔进火狱，那里全是孤恩者和反对真理者，</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "50:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>常不履行真主责成其义务者，僭越真主法度者，怀疑被告知的许诺和警告者，</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "50:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以及为真主设匹配并加以崇拜者。你们俩将他投进严厉的惩罚中吧。”</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "50:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那人的恶魔伙伴脱离和他干系说：“我们的主啊！我没有使他迷误，而是他自己处在远离真理的迷误之中。”</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "50:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主说：“你们不要在此争辩，那是无济于事的。在今世，我已为你们派遣众使者，带去了对不信道和悖逆之人的严厉警告。</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "50:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的言辞不能变更，我的许诺也不会爽约，我不会为亏枉他们，而减少他们的善功，增加他们的罪过，我必以他们的行为进行报酬。”</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "50:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，我对火狱说：“不信道和作恶者已将你填满了吗？”火狱回答它的养主说：“还有更多的吗？”</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "50:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>“乐园被移到遵从真主命令、远离真主禁令的敬畏者附近，他们可以看到其中的恩惠。</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "50:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音对他们说‘这就是真主给予每一位以忏悔回归祂、遵循祂命令的谨守之人的，</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "50:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>秘密的敬畏真主，并以健全之心向真主许诺者’，</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "50:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们平安地进入乐园吧！你们不会遭受所厌之事的困扰，那是永居之日的开始。”</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "50:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>乐园里，有他们所欲的永不罄尽的恩典，还有人类见所未见、闻所未闻、完全不可企及的恩典，其中就有眼见清高的真主。</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "50:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在麦加城这些不义者之前，我曾毁灭了多少否认使者的以物配主者啊！让他们在城镇中寻找吧，但愿他们找到躲避真主惩罚的一处逃避之所，他们绝不能找到！</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "50:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对上述民众的毁灭，对有心智的聆听之人，确是明显的提醒和劝告。</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "50:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>我确在六天内创造了诸天、大地及天地间的万物，我有能力在霎那间创造它们， 我没有像犹太教徒所说的那样感到一丝疲倦。</h2>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "50:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当坚忍犹太教徒和其他人说的妄言，当在日出前的晨礼中赞颂祂，日落前的哺礼时敬拜祂。</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "50:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当在夜间敬拜祂，在拜后赞颂祂。</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "50:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当倾听，在负责吹号角的天使在邻近之地呐喊，吹响第二声号角之日，</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "50:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>万物听到关于复活的呐喊之日，即是死人从坟墓走出接受清算和报酬之日。</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "50:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我使人生，使人死。除我外再没有掌握生死大权者。复活日，众仆必将回归于我，接受清算和报酬。</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "50:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>大地破裂而他们急速走出坟墓的日子，对我来说，那集合确是容易的。</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "50:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我彻知这些否认使者之人所说的谰言，使者啊！你并非被授权强迫他们信道，你只是传达真主命令你所传达的。你当以《古兰经》劝化和警告不信道和悖逆之人。惟恐惧者能聆听教诲，得以觉悟。</p>"
        }
    }
}